=Sweet Games =

24
00:01:47,184 --> 00:01:48,560
(One month later)

25
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,224
(Fragment Time Boyfriend)

26
00:01:50,226 --> 00:01:51,786
In my life,

27
00:01:51,786 --> 00:01:54,146
all the moments related to you

28
00:01:54,346 --> 00:01:56,506
seem particularly precious.

29
00:01:59,824 --> 00:02:04,048
(Game interface of
Fragment Time Boyfriend)

30
00:02:09,946 --> 00:02:10,586
Jiang Shan.

31
00:02:10,586 --> 00:02:11,666
Jiang Shan.

32
00:02:12,426 --> 00:02:13,266
Mr. Jiang,

33
00:02:13,346 --> 00:02:15,346
could you please sign for us?

34
00:02:15,346 --> 00:02:16,146
Sign here.

35
00:02:18,146 --> 00:02:18,786
Mr. Jiang,

36
00:02:18,786 --> 00:02:20,506
your voice is so pleasant,

37
00:02:20,506 --> 00:02:22,346
and you're so handsome.

38
00:02:23,226 --> 00:02:24,706
Okay, thank you, Mr. Jiang.

39
00:02:25,426 --> 00:02:26,546
Quick, give me the pen.

40
00:02:26,666 --> 00:02:27,986
The pen he touched.

41
00:02:28,706 --> 00:02:31,266
We're getting
more and more registered users now.

42
00:02:31,426 --> 00:02:32,666
At this rate,

43
00:02:32,866 --> 00:02:33,426
we'll soon

44
00:02:33,426 --> 00:02:35,866
be able to be on the top three of
the new games chart.

45
00:02:37,426 --> 00:02:38,506
Top three?

46
00:02:39,386 --> 00:02:40,426
I want to be number one.

47
00:02:41,266 --> 00:02:42,026
Ambitious.

48
00:02:43,226 --> 00:02:44,306
Look at the comments.

49
00:02:45,546 --> 00:02:47,266
Saying, "After playing

50
00:02:47,266 --> 00:02:48,546
'Fragment Time Boyfriend,'

51
00:02:49,026 --> 00:02:50,266
"my boyfriend
became more communicative."

52
00:02:52,546 --> 00:02:53,146
Oh, no.

53
00:02:54,106 --> 00:02:55,706
I have even less chance of
having a girlfriend now.

54
00:02:56,706 --> 00:02:58,106
Whether you're in a relationship,

55
00:02:58,106 --> 00:02:58,866
or single,

56
00:02:58,866 --> 00:03:00,106
what does it have to do with our game?

57
00:03:00,986 --> 00:03:01,506
What's more,

58
00:03:01,986 --> 00:03:02,586
they said,

59
00:03:02,586 --> 00:03:04,386
"Fragment Time Boyfriend"
doesn't push for in-game purchases,

60
00:03:04,386 --> 00:03:05,546
and promotes healthy life,

61
00:03:05,986 --> 00:03:07,506
which is refreshing
in the gaming industry.

62
00:03:08,106 --> 00:03:08,866
Look,

63
00:03:08,866 --> 00:03:11,986
many old players commented,

64
00:03:11,986 --> 00:03:14,986
they miss Mr. Heisha's voiceover.

65
00:03:49,261 --> 00:03:54,832
=Episode 17=
(Can't Have Both Love and Career)

66
00:03:56,706 --> 00:03:58,866
Complete the task I gave you well.

67
00:03:59,546 --> 00:04:00,586
Once it's done,

68
00:04:01,426 --> 00:04:03,266
you'll be rewarded.

69
00:04:10,426 --> 00:04:11,426
Let me introduce.

70
00:04:11,546 --> 00:04:14,266
This is the famous

71
00:04:14,266 --> 00:04:16,426
Zhao Qian from the Gaishi Group.

72
00:04:16,666 --> 00:04:17,146
Miss An.

73
00:04:17,146 --> 00:04:18,706
- Hello, Mr. Zhao.
- Hello.

74
00:04:19,706 --> 00:04:20,306
Miss An,

75
00:04:20,706 --> 00:04:21,986
I did some preliminary selection.

76
00:04:21,986 --> 00:04:23,826
We have a good candidate today.

77
00:04:24,106 --> 00:04:24,706
Really?

78
00:04:25,266 --> 00:04:28,106
(Resume of Chen Rui)
I'm glad you could come for an interview.

79
00:04:28,986 --> 00:04:30,146
I would like to know

80
00:04:30,146 --> 00:04:31,866
why you want to join our company.

81
00:04:42,706 --> 00:04:43,426
Miss Lan.

82
00:04:44,266 --> 00:04:44,866
An Ran.

83
00:04:45,306 --> 00:04:46,146
What would you like to drink?

84
00:04:46,866 --> 00:04:47,986
Lemon water.

85
00:04:47,986 --> 00:04:48,426
Thank you.

86
00:04:49,986 --> 00:04:51,586
You even made a special trip here.

87
00:04:52,146 --> 00:04:54,426
You could have the documents delivered.

88
00:04:55,706 --> 00:04:56,426
The board of directors

89
00:04:56,426 --> 00:04:57,706
needs to report it tomorrow.

90
00:04:57,986 --> 00:04:59,666
I just wanted to
help you look over it in advance.

91
00:04:59,706 --> 00:05:00,266
It's not a problem.

92
00:05:00,266 --> 00:05:01,706
Actually, I was nearby.

93
00:05:04,546 --> 00:05:05,266
Baby,

94
00:05:06,306 --> 00:05:07,146
are you home?

95
00:05:07,666 --> 00:05:08,546
How was it?

96
00:05:08,986 --> 00:05:09,586
Did you

97
00:05:09,586 --> 00:05:11,386
listen to the teachers
in the kindergarten today?

98
00:05:12,506 --> 00:05:13,986
Good girl.

99
00:05:15,266 --> 00:05:16,786
I will be home soon.

100
00:05:16,866 --> 00:05:17,986
Love you.

101
00:05:21,586 --> 00:05:22,546
What's wrong?

102
00:05:22,706 --> 00:05:24,106
Don't I look like a mother?

103
00:05:24,426 --> 00:05:26,386
I thought you were unmarried.

104
00:05:31,386 --> 00:05:32,986
She is so cute.

105
00:05:34,826 --> 00:05:36,026
You are so busy with work

106
00:05:36,026 --> 00:05:37,306
and taking care of her.

107
00:05:37,306 --> 00:05:38,386
It must be tiring, right?

108
00:05:40,026 --> 00:05:40,986
If I say it's not tiring,

109
00:05:40,986 --> 00:05:42,146
I am surely lying.

110
00:05:42,946 --> 00:05:43,946
Being a single mom

111
00:05:44,306 --> 00:05:45,946
is definitely a bit harder.

112
00:05:52,426 --> 00:05:53,826
May I ask

113
00:05:53,826 --> 00:05:55,106
where her father is?

114
00:05:55,666 --> 00:05:56,426
We broke up.

115
00:05:58,666 --> 00:06:00,106
He thought I was too dominant

116
00:06:00,266 --> 00:06:01,266
and he was unable control me.

117
00:06:01,706 --> 00:06:03,266
He wasn't willing to stay home
and take care of kid.

118
00:06:03,666 --> 00:06:05,506
How can we live like that?

119
00:06:07,266 --> 00:06:08,866
Then in the future...

120
00:06:09,386 --> 00:06:10,586
We'll just keep living like this.

121
00:06:11,386 --> 00:06:12,306
The child is with me.

122
00:06:12,306 --> 00:06:13,506
I wouldn't mistreat her.

123
00:06:14,506 --> 00:06:15,826
Who says a woman

124
00:06:15,826 --> 00:06:17,226
can't live well on her own?

125
00:06:21,266 --> 00:06:22,146
That's true.

126
00:06:23,506 --> 00:06:24,386
Give me the documents.

127
00:06:26,266 --> 00:06:28,026
The periodic report is tomorrow.

128
00:06:28,026 --> 00:06:29,226
I've already heard

129
00:06:29,386 --> 00:06:30,786
your launch

130
00:06:30,786 --> 00:06:32,026
is quite impressive.

131
00:06:33,026 --> 00:06:34,386
The results are okay.

132
00:06:34,826 --> 00:06:37,066
Mainly thanks to
your consistent support.

133
00:06:37,226 --> 00:06:37,986
Without you,

134
00:06:37,986 --> 00:06:39,746
there wouldn't be "Time Boyfriend" now.

135
00:06:39,906 --> 00:06:41,666
Mainly, you worked hard enough.

136
00:06:43,786 --> 00:06:44,346
An Ran,

137
00:06:46,546 --> 00:06:48,106
looking at you now,

138
00:06:48,306 --> 00:06:49,906
I feel like
I'm looking at myself in the past.

139
00:06:51,306 --> 00:06:52,986
Very competitive and determined.

140
00:06:57,986 --> 00:06:59,666
It's quite shameful.

141
00:07:00,306 --> 00:07:01,986
After all these years,

142
00:07:02,306 --> 00:07:05,346
it seems like
I've just embarked on the right track.

143
00:07:08,066 --> 00:07:10,186
Among all the variables in life,

144
00:07:10,786 --> 00:07:13,226
work is the most certain.

145
00:07:13,666 --> 00:07:14,866
As long as you work hard enough,

146
00:07:15,226 --> 00:07:15,986
sooner or later,

147
00:07:15,986 --> 00:07:17,226
there will be a reward.

148
00:07:20,346 --> 00:07:20,986
Come on.

149
00:07:22,346 --> 00:07:23,666
I wish everything goes well tomorrow.

150
00:07:52,786 --> 00:07:53,346
Yan Yue,

151
00:07:54,746 --> 00:07:56,106
when did you take this?

152
00:07:57,786 --> 00:07:58,906
The production team asked me to do so.

153
00:07:59,746 --> 00:08:00,306
How is it?

154
00:08:02,066 --> 00:08:04,186
So cool.

155
00:08:22,866 --> 00:08:23,466
Bro.

156
00:08:54,986 --> 00:08:56,866
If this happened to you,

157
00:08:57,226 --> 00:08:59,426
I believe you would
make the same choice as me.

158
00:09:00,746 --> 00:09:02,546
Something like romance

159
00:09:03,186 --> 00:09:05,106
won't affect your career, right?

160
00:09:15,866 --> 00:09:17,426
Did you two keep in touch afterward?

161
00:09:24,066 --> 00:09:25,466
Can you make it this time?

162
00:09:28,786 --> 00:09:29,626
I think

163
00:09:30,426 --> 00:09:32,786
I am at least better than
the last time I broke up.

164
00:09:35,186 --> 00:09:36,186
Significant improvement.

165
00:09:40,786 --> 00:09:42,906
There aren't any fundamental issues
between you,

166
00:09:42,906 --> 00:09:44,226
but why didn't you keep in touch?

167
00:09:47,466 --> 00:09:48,226
I don't know

168
00:09:49,106 --> 00:09:50,066
how to contact him.

169
00:09:51,546 --> 00:09:52,186
Why?

170
00:09:54,426 --> 00:09:55,666
Yan Yue stopped doing voice-overs

171
00:09:56,546 --> 00:09:57,786
because of me,

172
00:09:58,786 --> 00:10:00,866
and my work is a mess.

173
00:10:01,306 --> 00:10:02,666
What's the point of a relationship?

174
00:10:03,066 --> 00:10:04,666
What right do I have

175
00:10:04,986 --> 00:10:06,306
to contact him again?

176
00:10:08,546 --> 00:10:10,426
To adults,

177
00:10:11,906 --> 00:10:13,546
if both people are okay,

178
00:10:14,186 --> 00:10:15,106
everything is okay.

179
00:10:16,106 --> 00:10:17,866
But if one person is not okay,

180
00:10:18,626 --> 00:10:20,186
you even can't date.

181
00:10:21,186 --> 00:10:23,226
We'd better just focus on
what's in front of us.

182
00:10:25,786 --> 00:10:28,746
Did you know that
Miss Lan actually has a daughter?

183
00:10:30,306 --> 00:10:31,186
I've heard of that.

184
00:10:31,546 --> 00:10:32,866
I didn't know before.

185
00:10:34,226 --> 00:10:35,306
She thought

186
00:10:36,066 --> 00:10:37,106
I broke up with Yan Yue

187
00:10:37,106 --> 00:10:39,466
because I was afraid
that love would affect my work.

188
00:10:40,186 --> 00:10:41,426
She just doesn't understand you.

189
00:10:42,066 --> 00:10:43,786
It would be great if you could enjoy

190
00:10:43,786 --> 00:10:44,626
both a career and love.

191
00:10:49,466 --> 00:10:50,786
Enjoy both?

192
00:10:52,986 --> 00:10:54,106
It's indeed difficult.

193
00:11:06,130 --> 00:11:07,226
(Comments for Fragment Time Boyfriend)

194
00:11:07,226 --> 00:11:08,866
(This male lead is so cute.)

195
00:11:08,866 --> 00:11:10,186
(Although he's a bit immature,)

196
00:11:10,186 --> 00:11:11,426
(he's quite talented.)

197
00:11:11,426 --> 00:11:13,346
(I heard that
the character design of the male lead)

198
00:11:13,346 --> 00:11:15,226
(is very similar to
the voice actor, Heisha.)

199
00:11:15,226 --> 00:11:16,786
(Although Heisha has retired now,)

200
00:11:16,826 --> 00:11:17,666
(looking at it now,)

201
00:11:17,666 --> 00:11:19,986
(Heisha is just being honest.)

202
00:11:19,986 --> 00:11:21,626
(He is after all
a scandalous voice actor.)

203
00:11:21,626 --> 00:11:22,866
(It's right for him to retire.)

204
00:11:36,426 --> 00:11:37,106
Pay attention.

205
00:11:37,306 --> 00:11:39,226
First, you have to crush the soil.

206
00:11:40,306 --> 00:11:41,666
After crushing,

207
00:11:41,786 --> 00:11:44,306
take out the flowers
we want to cultivate.

208
00:11:48,426 --> 00:11:49,426
Life

209
00:11:49,426 --> 00:11:51,106
requires a bit of fun.

210
00:11:51,986 --> 00:11:53,746
Don't be all dressed up outside,

211
00:11:53,746 --> 00:11:55,346
and looking like a mess at home.

212
00:11:57,104 --> 00:11:59,120
♪You fill in my life♪

213
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:02,416
♪Can I write your name♪

214
00:12:02,608 --> 00:12:04,960
♪On my heart♪

215
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:07,376
♪Can I sing to you♪

216
00:12:07,376 --> 00:12:10,448
♪When times get dark♪

217
00:12:10,448 --> 00:12:13,168
♪Can I be the only one♪

218
00:12:13,168 --> 00:12:17,328
♪To kiss you goodnight♪

219
00:12:19,110 --> 00:12:23,056
♪It's better with you in my life♪

220
00:12:27,426 --> 00:12:27,786
Hello?

221
00:12:27,786 --> 00:12:29,106
Miss An, something's wrong.

222
00:12:29,106 --> 00:12:30,306
There's a problem with the game.

223
00:12:30,306 --> 00:12:31,226
Come to the company now.

224
00:12:43,666 --> 00:12:44,426
What happened?

225
00:12:44,426 --> 00:12:44,786
How did it

226
00:12:44,786 --> 00:12:45,986
get attacked out of the blue?

227
00:12:46,426 --> 00:12:47,546
Changfeng is investigating.

228
00:12:47,786 --> 00:12:49,666
All the loopholes were fixed
before the launch.

229
00:12:49,666 --> 00:12:50,626
It was normal yesterday,

230
00:12:50,786 --> 00:12:52,226
and suddenly like this today.

231
00:12:52,546 --> 00:12:54,226
Before I got off work,
I specifically logged into the game,

232
00:12:54,226 --> 00:12:55,306
and set up a CDN defense,

233
00:12:55,306 --> 00:12:56,746
even including the Netplay server,

234
00:12:56,906 --> 00:12:58,546
just to deal with such an emergency.

235
00:12:59,346 --> 00:13:01,466
Can you locate the attacker now?

236
00:13:01,786 --> 00:13:02,786
The attack was without warning.

237
00:13:02,986 --> 00:13:04,306
The company's firewall perception

238
00:13:04,306 --> 00:13:05,306
didn't even alert.

239
00:13:05,786 --> 00:13:07,306
So, it's impossible
to locate the other party.

240
00:13:09,226 --> 00:13:10,986
Could it be another company,

241
00:13:10,986 --> 00:13:12,426
seeing our game is so popular,

242
00:13:12,426 --> 00:13:13,866
so they hired a hacker to attack?

243
00:13:16,346 --> 00:13:17,666
Probably not.

244
00:13:18,106 --> 00:13:19,226
It could just be

245
00:13:19,226 --> 00:13:20,666
a common virus
the hacker sprayed and prayed.

246
00:13:21,106 --> 00:13:22,306
Isn't it a common risk

247
00:13:22,306 --> 00:13:23,986
faced by game companies?

248
00:13:26,306 --> 00:13:27,626
Our top priority now

249
00:13:27,626 --> 00:13:29,546
is to get the game back online
as soon as possible.

250
00:13:29,546 --> 00:13:29,986
Changfeng,

251
00:13:29,986 --> 00:13:30,906
do you have any other solutions?

252
00:13:31,986 --> 00:13:33,226
I need some time.

253
00:13:33,226 --> 00:13:33,786
How many days?

254
00:13:35,306 --> 00:13:35,986
Miss An,

255
00:13:36,546 --> 00:13:37,986
there's an email in the work inbox,

256
00:13:37,986 --> 00:13:39,106
saying they'll stop attacking the game

257
00:13:39,106 --> 00:13:40,546
if we give them 200 thousand yuan.

258
00:13:40,986 --> 00:13:41,866
200 thousand?

259
00:13:42,546 --> 00:13:44,106
It might be a professional hacker.

260
00:13:52,666 --> 00:13:53,986
Should I borrow some money?

261
00:13:54,786 --> 00:13:55,426
No way.

262
00:13:55,786 --> 00:13:56,666
Why should you do that?

263
00:13:56,986 --> 00:13:58,546
Paying is the worst plan.

264
00:13:59,306 --> 00:14:00,106
Miss An is right.

265
00:14:00,866 --> 00:14:02,466
Paying will only make them extort more.

266
00:14:03,786 --> 00:14:05,426
Give me some time to operate.

267
00:14:06,106 --> 00:14:06,866
Rui,

268
00:14:07,186 --> 00:14:08,666
you know the market better.

269
00:14:08,666 --> 00:14:10,226
Do you know

270
00:14:10,226 --> 00:14:11,226
how other companies

271
00:14:11,226 --> 00:14:12,226
resolve this kind of situation?

272
00:14:13,426 --> 00:14:13,906
I...

273
00:14:15,226 --> 00:14:16,986
I-I don't know.

274
00:14:20,106 --> 00:14:20,666
How about this?

275
00:14:20,866 --> 00:14:22,226
Hu Yingjun and I will go to the police.

276
00:14:23,346 --> 00:14:23,786
Let's go.

277
00:14:37,066 --> 00:14:37,426
Hello?

278
00:14:37,666 --> 00:14:38,306
An Ran,

279
00:14:38,306 --> 00:14:39,986
I heard about the game.

280
00:14:39,986 --> 00:14:41,546
What countermeasures do you have now?

281
00:14:43,866 --> 00:14:44,866
We don't have any for now.

282
00:14:45,306 --> 00:14:46,306
I'm still on a business trip.

