00:14:46,426 --> 00:14:47,666
As soon as I land tomorrow,

284
00:14:47,666 --> 00:14:48,866
we'll have a meeting immediately.

285
00:14:51,226 --> 00:14:51,746
Okay.

286
00:15:02,066 --> 00:15:03,226
Miss An, get some rest early.

287
00:15:03,626 --> 00:15:04,306
Goodbye, Miss An.

288
00:15:04,546 --> 00:15:05,466
Bye, Mr. Hu.

289
00:15:05,466 --> 00:15:06,546
Bye, bye.

290
00:15:06,546 --> 00:15:07,666
Bye, Miss An.

291
00:15:07,666 --> 00:15:08,226
Bye.

292
00:15:46,346 --> 00:15:47,466
What should we do, bro?

293
00:15:50,586 --> 00:15:51,586
We really don't pay?

294
00:15:52,586 --> 00:15:53,466
How do we pay?

295
00:15:54,586 --> 00:15:56,346
How much money do we have?

296
00:15:59,866 --> 00:16:01,706
They just target

297
00:16:01,706 --> 00:16:03,346
small companies with no backing like us

298
00:16:04,106 --> 00:16:05,946
