299
00:16:06,946 --> 00:16:09,106
We don't even
have the strength to resist.

300
00:16:11,826 --> 00:16:13,946
Isn't this exactly what hackers aim for?

301
00:16:20,586 --> 00:16:22,106
After struggling for so many years,

302
00:16:22,106 --> 00:16:23,706
and finally seeing a bit of success,

303
00:16:24,466 --> 00:16:25,186
I thought

304
00:16:25,786 --> 00:16:26,226
I finally

305
00:16:26,226 --> 00:16:28,106
could stand firm in Hu's family.

306
00:16:29,426 --> 00:16:31,586
But who knew such a curveball
would come halfway?

307
00:16:34,786 --> 00:16:35,866
"Time Boyfriend"

308
00:16:36,586 --> 00:16:38,186
is the fruit of our years of labors.

309
00:16:39,986 --> 00:16:41,426
I won't let it fail.

310
00:16:43,786 --> 00:16:44,426
Hu,

311
00:16:44,826 --> 00:16:46,106
you must believe in yourself

312
00:16:47,226 --> 00:16:48,186
and others.

313
00:16:50,226 --> 00:16:51,066
We can make it.

314
00:16:56,066 --> 00:16:56,866
I believe in you.

315
00:17:32,937 --> 00:17:35,388
(Wayward Courage)

316
00:17:36,706 --> 00:17:38,706
(I don't like a life
that's predictable.)

317
00:17:39,466 --> 00:17:41,066
(We use courage as a chip,)

318
00:17:41,426 --> 00:17:43,346
(and leave our hometowns ambitiously.)

319
00:17:44,586 --> 00:17:46,186
(But when the real unknown)

320
00:17:46,186 --> 00:17:48,106
(comes rushing in like a dark tide,)

321
00:17:49,346 --> 00:17:50,586
(we have nowhere to hide.)

322
00:17:51,986 --> 00:17:52,826
(Fear,)

323
00:17:53,106 --> 00:17:53,826
(regret,)

324
00:17:54,306 --> 00:17:54,826
(and confusion)

325
00:17:54,826 --> 00:17:56,866
(push us gamblers into a corner.)

326
00:17:58,466 --> 00:17:59,546
(Only then we realize)

327
00:18:00,346 --> 00:18:00,986
