328
00:18:00,986 --> 00:18:02,866
(a bill recklessness is.)

329
00:18:06,466 --> 00:18:08,186
(What can we use
to pay for recklessness?)

330
00:18:09,786 --> 00:18:11,106
(For those drowning in debt,)

331
00:18:11,946 --> 00:18:13,946
(if you still have a few guts
in your pocket,)

332
00:18:14,586 --> 00:18:16,306
(take them out bravely.)

333
00:18:17,866 --> 00:18:19,066
(The last chip)

334
00:18:19,346 --> 00:18:20,866
