proposed by them.

339
00:19:05,826 --> 00:19:07,066
Because of the finances?

340
00:19:10,226 --> 00:19:11,226
Greed is hard to satisfy.

341
00:19:11,466 --> 00:19:13,786
If it happens once,
it will definitely happen a second time.

342
00:19:15,666 --> 00:19:17,426
But what we are considering now is

343
00:19:17,426 --> 00:19:18,706
players have been unable
to log in to the game

344
00:19:18,706 --> 00:19:19,946
for more than a day.

345
00:19:20,306 --> 00:19:21,946
If this continues,

346
00:19:21,986 --> 00:19:23,466
it will be a complete loss of players.

347
00:19:23,666 --> 00:19:24,706
When it goes online again,

348
00:19:24,866 --> 00:19:26,466
all the previous efforts will be wasted.

349
00:19:27,546 --> 00:19:28,186
An Ran,

350
00:19:29,306 --> 00:19:30,866
