356
00:19:51,920 --> 00:20:00,496
(Text from an unknown number:
Understood, proceed as planned.)

357
00:20:00,666 --> 00:20:01,306
Rui.

358
00:20:04,426 --> 00:20:05,066
What's wrong with you?

359
00:20:05,066 --> 00:20:06,306
You look so pale.

360
00:20:07,426 --> 00:20:07,986
Nothing.

361
00:20:07,986 --> 00:20:09,666
I probably didn't rest well yesterday.

362
00:20:09,666 --> 00:20:10,666
Eat something.

363
00:20:10,666 --> 00:20:11,226
Thanks.

364
00:20:11,226 --> 00:20:12,186
I finally know the reason.

365
00:20:13,306 --> 00:20:14,226
Why?

366
00:20:17,426 --> 00:20:17,986
Our bandwidth

367
00:20:17,986 --> 00:20:19,546
has been consumed by attack packets
from different

368
00:20:19,546 --> 00:20:20,186
addresses.

369
00:20:20,466 --> 00:20:22,106
This has caused the server
to not function properly.

370
00:20:22,306 --> 00:20:24,186
It is a large-scale organized attack.

371
00:20:25,546 --> 00:20:28,106
What should we do now?

372
00:20:32,986 --> 00:20:34,466
Either strengthen
the system's protection,

373
00:20:35,186 --> 00:20:36,826
