384
00:21:05,786 --> 00:21:07,826
we will only lose our say.

385
00:21:08,186 --> 00:21:09,466
Moreover, "Time Boyfriend"

386
00:21:09,466 --> 00:21:10,586
will likely be turned into

387
00:21:10,586 --> 00:21:11,706
another game by them.

388
00:21:11,986 --> 00:21:13,426
Upgrading the server

389
