390
00:21:15,946 --> 00:21:18,306
Extortion is a crime in itself.

391
00:21:18,306 --> 00:21:18,986
I understand why

392
00:21:18,986 --> 00:21:20,546
companies with the same experience as us

393
00:21:20,546 --> 00:21:21,866
don't dare to stand up.

394
00:21:21,866 --> 00:21:22,706
But I...

395
00:21:23,586 --> 00:21:24,706
I'm willing

396
00:21:24,866 --> 00:21:25,786
to take the risk.

397
00:21:25,786 --> 00:21:27,106
I'm also willing to stand up.

398
00:21:27,106 --> 00:21:28,426
If there's a chance,

399
00:21:28,866 --> 00:21:30,226
I want to clean up

400
00:21:30,226 --> 00:21:31,546
all the demons and monsters
in this industry.

401
00:21:35,426 --> 00:21:35,986
Take the risk?

402
00:21:37,466 --> 00:21:38,426
How?

403
00:21:39,306 --> 00:21:41,546
You don't even know
who your opponent is.

404
00:21:43,106 --> 00:21:46,106
We are just in the initial stages
of being attacked.

405
00:21:46,666 --> 00:21:47,586
If we go offline directly,

406
00:21:47,946 --> 00:21:49,426
they will definitely
let down their guard,

407
00:21:49,426 --> 00:21:50,426
and then reveal their weakness.

408
00:21:50,786 --> 00:21:52,666
The internet is not a lawless place.

409
00:21:53,546 --> 00:21:55,066
We just need time.

410
00:21:55,306 --> 00:21:55,826
Alright.

411
00:21:56,226 --> 00:21:57,826
Even if we implement your method,

412
00:21:58,226 --> 00:21:59,346
once you find them,

413
00:21:59,546 --> 00:22:00,986
