00:22:03,066 --> 00:22:03,666
An Ran,

416
00:22:04,466 --> 00:22:05,786
I need to remind you.

417
00:22:06,186 --> 00:22:06,986
Lansheng

418
00:22:08,106 --> 00:22:09,346
is in the business of investing,

419
00:22:10,106 --> 00:22:11,346
