420
00:22:15,786 --> 00:22:16,426
An Ran,

421
00:22:17,346 --> 00:22:18,586
"Fragment Time Boyfriend"

422
00:22:18,706 --> 00:22:20,466
is the only and the one

423
00:22:20,466 --> 00:22:21,826
independently designed game made by you.

424
00:22:22,186 --> 00:22:23,066
I think for its meaning to you

425
00:22:23,066 --> 00:22:24,666
and Gaishi Unparalleled,

426
00:22:24,666 --> 00:22:26,466
no one knows it better than you.

427
00:22:27,106 --> 00:22:29,466
I hope you can consider it carefully.

428
00:22:33,986 --> 00:22:36,346
It's precisely because
"Fragment Time Boyfriend"

429
00:22:36,546 --> 00:22:37,866
and Gaishi Unparalleled

430
00:22:38,666 --> 00:22:40,346
are of extraordinary significance to me.

431
00:22:41,346 --> 00:22:41,986
That's why

432
00:22:42,546 --> 00:22:43,866
I made this decision.

433
00:22:45,266 --> 00:22:47,386
Switching to a single-player game
is just temporary,

434
00:22:48,026 --> 00:22:50,386
but it is currently the best method.

435
00:22:57,106 --> 00:22:57,786
Mr. Hu.

436
00:22:59,746 --> 00:23:00,426
In fact,

437
00:23:00,426 --> 00:23:02,906
you are the biggest shareholder.

438
00:23:03,866 --> 00:23:05,266
I want your opinion.

439
00:23:11,986 --> 00:23:12,546
Miss Lan,

440
00:23:13,226 --> 00:23:13,906
Mr. Pei,

441
00:23:14,986 --> 00:23:16,626
although I am the biggest shareholder

442
00:23:16,626 --> 00:23:17,746
of "Fragment Time Boyfriend",

443
00:23:18,226 --> 00:23:18,786
An Ran

444
00:23:18,786 --> 00:23:20,746
is the soul of "Time Boyfriend."

445
00:23:21,226 --> 00:23:22,626
I support An Ran's decision.

446
00:23:22,986 --> 00:23:24,346
Refund the players' recharges

447
00:23:24,346 --> 00:23:26,106
and temporarily switch to
single-player operation.

448
00:23:29,546 --> 00:23:30,226
Okay.

449
00:23:31,506 --> 00:23:33,346
Since you've already made this decision,

450
00:23:34,026 --> 00:23:35,506
then let's do as you propose.

451
00:23:37,426 --> 00:23:39,026
But we also have rules in our company.

452
00:23:39,346 --> 00:23:41,386
When a public relations crisis arises,

453
00:23:41,746 --> 00:23:43,546
