from the CEO of the invested company,

455
00:23:46,546 --> 00:23:47,666
so that our invested company

456
00:23:47,666 --> 00:23:49,626
can smoothly overcome the crisis.

457
00:23:51,346 --> 00:23:52,226
So Mr. Hu,

458
00:23:52,986 --> 00:23:54,026
next,

459
00:23:54,026 --> 00:23:55,986
you may need to cooperate with Mr. Pei

460
00:23:56,866 --> 00:23:58,866
to let us take over

461
00:23:59,226 --> 00:24:00,546
Gaishi Unparalleled for now.

462
00:24:04,386 --> 00:24:05,226
An Ran,

463
00:24:06,346 --> 00:24:07,666
you also need a rest.

464
00:24:18,986 --> 00:24:19,626
An Ran,

465
00:24:20,426 --> 00:24:22,106
I advise you to reconsider.

466
00:24:35,426 --> 00:24:37,426
"Fragment Time Boyfriend"
has announced its server shutdown.

467
00:24:37,746 --> 00:24:39,746
I heard it was attacked by hackers,

468
00:24:39,746 --> 00:24:40,866
