504
00:26:45,346 --> 00:26:46,666
I-I'd better not.

505
00:26:46,666 --> 00:26:47,506
It's settled then.

506
00:26:48,866 --> 00:26:49,986
I have to go.

507
00:26:50,346 --> 00:26:52,226
