00:32:47,626 --> 00:32:49,346
Look at the bathroom and kitchen,

563
00:32:49,346 --> 00:32:50,706
all connected to your bedroom.

564
00:32:50,706 --> 00:32:52,266
What's the smell of
the quilts and mattresses?

565
00:32:52,626 --> 00:32:53,786
You haven't thrown the trash.

566
00:32:56,946 --> 00:32:59,346
Why don't you
open the windows for ventilation?

567
00:33:02,626 --> 00:33:03,706
Have you had breakfast yet?

568
00:33:05,546 --> 00:33:06,866
Why are you eating takeout again?

569
00:33:08,186 --> 00:33:09,106
I bought it yesterday.

570
00:33:10,786 --> 00:33:12,706
Tell me what you want to eat.

571
00:33:16,346 --> 00:33:17,186
Spicy noodles.

572
00:33:19,026 --> 00:33:20,346
Your mom has brought them for you.

573
00:33:22,546 --> 00:33:23,706
The noodles will be ready in a while.

574
00:33:23,946 --> 00:33:25,106
Wash up.

575
00:33:58,106 --> 00:33:59,506
Here come the noodles.

576
00:34:01,346 --> 00:34:01,986
Here.

577
00:34:09,466 --> 00:34:10,386
Eat while it's hot.

578
00:34:25,266 --> 00:34:26,706
Still the same taste, right?

579
00:34:32,506 --> 00:34:34,186
Take your time.

580
00:34:44,226 --> 00:34:45,706
Why are you crying?

581
00:34:53,746 --> 00:34:55,346
I am here, right?

582
00:35:02,426 --> 00:35:03,946
Our Ran has grown up.

583
00:35:04,466 --> 00:35:06,946
If you want to
have a pair of strong wings,

584
00:35:07,986 --> 00:35:10,106
you must face it with tenacity.

585
00:35:10,946 --> 00:35:12,186
These are the bumps

586
00:35:12,546 --> 00:35:14,466
that one must experience in life.

587
00:35:17,466 --> 00:35:19,026
I know my own daughter.

588
00:35:20,266 --> 00:35:21,466
I believe in you.

589
00:35:26,466 --> 00:35:27,186
Eat up.

590
00:35:30,466 --> 00:35:32,546
I want to eat braised pork for lunch.

591
00:35:32,786 --> 00:35:33,706
Okay.

592
00:35:35,186 --> 00:35:38,026
I will make you braised pork for lunch.

593
00:35:39,066 --> 00:35:39,706
Eat up.

594
00:36:06,946 --> 00:36:07,506
Ran,

595
00:36:08,866 --> 00:36:10,706
I have a few words to say to you.

596
00:36:12,986 --> 00:36:15,506
Even if you're busy at work outside,

597
00:36:16,186 --> 00:36:17,426
you can't always stay up late.

598
00:36:18,106 --> 00:36:19,346
Eat less takeout.

599
00:36:19,866 --> 00:36:20,986
Take good care of your health.

600
00:36:23,946 --> 00:36:25,946
Here, take this.

601
00:36:25,946 --> 00:36:28,026
No, no, Dad. I can't accept this.

602
00:36:28,186 --> 00:36:30,106
It's only natural to accept
what your parents give you.

603
00:36:30,466 --> 00:36:33,146
Besides, it's not easy
being alone outside.

604
00:36:33,466 --> 00:36:34,506
If you don't take this,

605
00:36:35,186 --> 00:36:36,746
can your mother rest easy?

606
00:36:38,106 --> 00:36:38,666
Take it.

607
00:36:41,026 --> 00:36:42,946
Rest early. I'm leaving now.

608
00:36:43,186 --> 00:36:44,506
Dad, you're leaving now?

609
00:36:45,106 --> 00:36:46,466
Your mother has something to do
and can't leave.

610
00:36:47,866 --> 00:36:49,266
She's also worried at home,

611
00:36:49,626 --> 00:36:51,146
so I have to rush back

612
00:36:51,146 --> 00:36:52,466
and report your situation to her.

613
00:36:53,186 --> 00:36:55,386
Then tell her
everything is fine with me.

614
00:36:55,386 --> 00:36:56,746
- Okay.
- You guys take care of yourselves.

615
00:36:58,186 --> 00:36:58,786
Alright.

616
00:36:59,186 --> 00:36:59,946
Go back.

617
00:37:06,346 --> 00:37:07,626
(We were rebellious,)

618
00:37:08,146 --> 00:37:10,226
(thinking our parents' wings
were shackles.)

619
00:37:11,626 --> 00:37:12,626
(After struggling to break free,)

620
00:37:12,626 --> 00:37:14,666
(we wanted to roam freely in the world.)

621
00:37:15,746 --> 00:37:16,826
(After being whipped)

622
00:37:16,826 --> 00:37:19,786
(by the harsh reality, we realized)

623
00:37:20,946 --> 00:37:22,906
(that our parents are still behind us,)

624
00:37:23,586 --> 00:37:24,386
(watching,)

625
00:37:25,106 --> 00:37:25,826
(guarding,)

626
00:37:26,586 --> 00:37:27,506
(and protecting us.)

627
00:37:50,906 --> 00:37:53,506
Hey, old classmate. It's me, You Mai.

628
00:37:53,866 --> 00:37:54,546
I know.

629
00:37:55,106 --> 00:37:55,946
Are you free later?

630
00:37:55,946 --> 00:37:57,866
I invite you out for a drink. My treat.

631
00:37:59,186 --> 00:38:00,466
Don't be silent.

632
00:38:00,986 --> 00:38:02,746
I have something important to say.

633
00:38:03,146 --> 00:38:04,546
My friends and I

634
00:38:04,546 --> 00:38:07,466
are making animations.
Traditional Chinese style. It's reliable.

635
00:38:07,626 --> 00:38:08,946
I'm now the sound director,

636
00:38:09,146 --> 00:38:10,266
but I lack

637
00:38:10,266 --> 00:38:12,426
a voice acting master like you
to do the dubbing.

638
00:38:12,666 --> 00:38:13,786
What do you think? Do you want to come?

639
00:38:14,386 --> 00:38:15,346
I'll pass.

640
00:38:15,626 --> 00:38:17,706
Don't reject me so soon.

641
00:38:18,186 --> 00:38:20,626
You need to do some new projects,

642
00:38:20,626 --> 00:38:22,746
change your mood, and make new friends.

643
00:38:22,746 --> 00:38:23,626
When you are busy,

644
00:38:23,626 --> 00:38:25,506
won't you forget
all those unhappy things?

645
00:38:26,906 --> 00:38:27,786
Let me think about it.

646
00:38:28,226 --> 00:38:30,146
Alright, then I'll invite them out.

647
00:38:31,386 --> 00:38:33,666
I said, "Let me think about it."

648
00:38:34,026 --> 00:38:35,946
Alright, you think.

649
00:38:35,946 --> 00:38:37,186
I'm on my way to find you.

650
00:38:37,466 --> 00:38:38,026
Wait for me.

651
00:39:09,440 --> 00:39:14,048
♪A movie, full of twists and turns
multiple plots♪

652
00:39:16,321 --> 00:39:21,760
♪But you and I have only
one possibility♪

653
00:39:23,530 --> 00:39:28,320
♪Our relationship is complicated
separated by thousands of miles♪

654
00:39:29,289 --> 00:39:31,904
