655
00:39:31,904 --> 00:39:35,648
♪Where should I stand♪

656
00:39:35,648 --> 00:39:37,664
♪From the strange to the familiar♪

657
00:39:37,664 --> 00:39:40,288
♪From the familiar to the strange,
it's an inevitable part of love♪

658
